findings.message:
Use 'container.createSpan({
      cls: `codex-process-file-link codex-process-file-link-${file.kind} ${extraClass}`.trim(),
      text: label,
      attr: {
        role: "button",
        tabindex: "0",
        title: file.displayPath,
        "aria-label": `打开 ${label}`
      }
    })' instead of 'container.createEl("span", {
      cls: `codex-process-file-link codex-process-file-link-${file.kind} ${extraClass}`.trim(),
      text: label,
      attr: {
        role: "button",
        tabindex: "0",
        title: file.displayPath,
        "aria-label": `打开 ${label}`
      }
    })'.
